TI  - Economic analysis of the intercropping of lettuce and tomato in different seasons under protected cultivation
JO  - Hortic. Bras.
T2  - Hortic. Bras.
PY  - 2010
VL  - 28
IS  - 3
SP  - 326
EP  - 336
DO  - 10.1590/S0102-05362010000300015
