TI  - Cultivo de abóbora, suplementada com biofertilizante, em aléias de leguminosas arbóreas X1 - Pumpkin cultivation, supplemented with biofertilizer, in alleys cropping of leguminous trees
JO  - Hortic. Bras.
T2  - Hortic. Bras.
PY  - 2015
VL  - 33
IS  - 1
SP  - 40
EP  - 44
DO  - 10.1590/S0102-053620150000100007
