TI  - Effects of potato (<i>Solanum tuberosum</i> L.)-<i>Mucuna pruriens</i> intercropping pattern on the agronomic performances of potato and the soil physicochemical properties of the western highlands of Cameroon
PY  - 2023
VL  - 8
IS  - 1
SP  - 20220142
